### Reg-Tech API — Analytics & Insights Endpoints (Layer 4)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = <paste-ta-jwt-here>

### ─── Dashboard Metrics ───
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/dashboard?jurisdiction=IE&from=2024-01-01&to=2024-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── Country Comparison ───
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/countries?countries=IE,GB,DE&reportingPeriod=2024
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── Anomaly Detection ───
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/anomalies?jurisdiction=IE&severity=HIGH
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ─── Full-Text Search ───
POST {{baseUrl}}/analytics/search
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Schneider GmbH",
  "filters": {
    "filingType": "CRS",
    "reportingPeriod": "2024",
    "jurisdiction": "DE"
  },
  "page": 1,
  "limit": 25
}

###

### ─── FI Performance Metrics ───
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/dashboard?organizationId=00000000-0000-4000-a000-000000000004
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
